  "title": "Chef (Chinese Cuisine)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and cook a variety of Chinese dishes according to the menu.</li>\n  <li>Master the control of heat for different cooking techniques.</li>\n  <li>Ensure food quality and presentation meet company standards.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the kitchen and cooking equipment.</li>\n  <li>Manage ingredient preparation and ensure all supplies are fresh and of high quality.</li>\n  <li>Monitor inventory and coordinate orders with suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Comply with health and safety regulations, including HACCP and 5S standards.</li>\n  <li>Assist in menu planning and development of new dishes.</li>\n  <li>Train and supervise kitchen staff as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>",
